{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_04_03",
  "title": "神崎莉央 3話 チャンスは決して逃がさない！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――写真撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Day of photo shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "映画の雰囲気に一番合いそうな衣装を\n選んでみたんだけど、どうかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I picked out a costume that seems to fit the mood of the movie best.\nWhat do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "よく似合ってますよ\nこれならケイティにも負けていません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It suits you well.\nWith this‚ you won't be losing out to Katy at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "彼女はこんなものじゃないわ！\nケイティをバカにしないで！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She's not just this‚ you know!\nDon't underestimate Katy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "褒めたのに怒られた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got scolded even though I was complimenting…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "まったく……\n貴方はケイティへのリスペクトが足りないのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really…\nYou're lacking respect for Katy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "ところで、今日のために仕上げてきた\n私の体はどうかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ how about the body\nI've worked up for today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "どう、この力こぶ。貴方よりあるんじゃないかしら\n腹筋もカチカチよ。触ってみる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How's this for biceps? Think they might be bigger than yours?\nMy abs are rock-solid‚ too. Want to feel?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、さすがに触るのはやめておきます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I'd rather not touch…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……。とはいえ、ここまで体を作り込むのは\nちょっと女の子らしくなかったかもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha… Although‚ maybe getting this ripped\nwasn't too girly of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺は莉央さんらしくていいと思いますよ\n撮影のために頑張った証ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it's very much like you‚ Rio-san. It's proof of your hard work for the shoot.\nI think it's very much like you‚ Rio-san. It's proof of your hard work for the shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう\nそろそろ撮影が始まるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you.\nThe shooting is about to start.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "見ていてね。ケイティそっくりとはいかないけど\n私らしいクールな写真にしてみせるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Watch me. I may not be the spitting image of Katy‚\nbut I'll show you a cool photo shoot that's uniquely me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影が終わって、数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――a few days after the shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 69.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "この間撮影した写真の画像が送られてきたので\n一緒に確認してもらっていいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've received the photos from the other day's shoot‚\ncan we take a look at them together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "もう写真が出来上がったの？\nどんな仕上がりになったのか楽しみだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The photos are ready already?\nI'm excited to see how they turned out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……いいじゃない、これ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… ain't they somethin'‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "まるで映画のワンシーンみたいね\n今にも作品が始まりそうだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's like a scene straight outta a movie.\nFeels like the story's about to start any second now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "衣装もばっちりハマっていて\n頑張って体を鍛えた甲斐がありましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The costume's a perfect fit‚\nand all the effort you put into toning your body paid off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "そっくりとはいかなかったけど\n体を絞って、殺陣を勉強して、ポーズを研究して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I might not be her spitting image‚\nbut I slimmed down‚ studied up on the fight scenes‚ perfected the poses…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "最高の一枚を撮るためにやれることは全部やったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did everything I could to make sure we got the best shot possible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "この撮影のために私が陰で努力をしていたなんて\n見ている人は気付かないでしょうね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Folks looking at these photos might not realize\nall the work I put into it behind the scenes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.5333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "……私はケイティのように\nヒロインの魅力をちゃんと表現出来たかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Wonder if I managed to capture the charm of a heroine‚\nlike Katy did?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "クールで格好いいヒロインの魅力が伝わってくる\n莉央さんらしい、いい写真ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The cool and stylish charm of a heroine comes through‚\nit's a great picture that's very you‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "仕事で好きな映画に携われるなんて\nこんなことが出来るのもアイドルならではね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be involved in a movie I love through my work‚\nthat's something only an idol can experience‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "私はこの写真に映画への想いを込めた……\n写真を見た人に、私の想いは伝わるかしら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I poured my love for the movie into this photo…\nI wonder if that feeling comes across to the people who see it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "想いはきっと伝わりますよ\nその証拠に、これを見て下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your feelings will surely come across.\nAnd as proof‚ take a look at this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "これは……映画の宣伝部から私宛てにメール？\nええと、「急なご連絡で失礼します」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this… an email to me from the movie's publicity department?\nUh‚ \"We apologize for the sudden contact‚\"",
        "id": ""
      },
