    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "「現在、映画のプロモーションのために\nケイティが来日しているのですが」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Currently‚ for the promotion of the movie‚\nKaty is visiting Japan‚\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "「ケイティに今回の写真を見せたところ、大絶賛で\nぜひ神崎さんに会ってみたいと言って……」ええっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"She saw the recent photos and was incredibly impressed‚\nand she said she would love to meet Ms. Kanzaki…\" What?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "どうやら、来日中のケイティが\n莉央さんに会いたがっているみたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems that Katy‚ who is visiting Japan‚\nwants to meet you‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、彼女は過密スケジュールで、今すぐホテルに\n行かないと会えないみたいですが……どうしますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But she has a packed schedule and if we don't go to her hotel right away‚\nwe might miss the chance… What do you want to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "え……今からケイティに会う？　……待って。無理",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… Meet Katy now? Wait… that's impossible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "無理ですか。急な話だし仕方ないですね\n分かりました。俺から断りの連絡を入れておきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Impossible‚ huh? It is sudden‚ so it can't be helped.\nAlright. I'll send a message to decline.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.2333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと待って。何勝手に断ろうとしてるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait a second. Why are you deciding to decline on your own?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "え？　でも今無理って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? But you just said it was impossible…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの「無理」はそういう意味じゃないわ！\n会いに行くに決まってるでしょ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The \"impossible\" I said wasn't what you think!\nOf course‚ I'm going to meet her!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_03-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "憧れのハリウッドスターに会えるチャンスなんて\n二度とないかもしれないんだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A chance to meet my Hollywood star idol may\nnever come again…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
